This documentation page details how to send Amplitude cohorts to Google Ads for creating targeted audience segments, including setup requirements, three upload key types (Contact Info, Mobile Advertising ID, and CRM ID), and the step-by-step process for syncing cohorts with considerations for processing time and privacy thresholds.

